{"tid":314043,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"大家覺得幼女戰記好睇定終末的伊澤塔好睇?","createTime":"2017-07-08T23:41:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-19T10:15:48.000Z","uid":80323,"like":24,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5aa4e58efd360e6b08eeba03f24f3baa7319f6e8","tid":314043,"uid":80323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T23:41:44.000Z","msg":"正評   幼女戰記<br />\n負評   終末的伊澤<br />\n<br />\n我覺得幼女戰記好過終末的伊澤塔，幼女戰記打仗打足好多集，反而伊澤塔出場打幾分鐘就完，第五集佢出場3分鐘就打完，戰術係好但係幾分鐘就完真係無癮<br />\n。好多時間就播其他D日常百合情節。<br />\n<br />\n終末的伊澤塔個公主係戰場對住成班士兵講野。又住係城堡到，完全唔似現代國家。<br />\n幼女戰記有城市戰同民兵打仗，原本想結束戰爭結果到最尾引黎更多國家參戰，劇情好過伊澤塔。<br />\n仲有伊澤塔既BGM比較怪"},{"pid":"e260dc5214b9de0dc7211472d3e02e47d243f2c2","tid":314043,"uid":47475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T16:24:10.000Z","msg":"一套係改編，一套係原創，都唔使問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw, 近幾年原創動畫冇乜好嘢(雖然light novel改編都唔好得幾多)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffd4f16da5b47f4d9930268237466ab7ce4929db","tid":314043,"uid":1531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T16:31:07.000Z","msg":"伊澤我睇完第1集就無睇...<br />\n<br />\n同樣有早見我都頂唔緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"114888d1649ef6d6aed0ba86cb2959804473b231","tid":314043,"uid":100412,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T16:33:22.000Z","msg":"伊澤塔高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n美中不足就係伊澤塔最後竟然唔使死<br />\n利申 無睇幼女"},{"pid":"c233a978554e610dbffe31ebaf788e966e52f689","tid":314043,"uid":100412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T16:35:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一套係改編，一套係原創，都唔使問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw, 近幾年原創動畫冇乜好嘢(雖然light novel改編都唔好得幾多)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSAKURA QUEST 如何？<br />\n開頭係悶啲，但現時係漸入佳境"},{"pid":"c93d6af0b8894750d15e5874ac4e61f60cd72b12","tid":314043,"uid":30745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T16:35:48.000Z","msg":"兩樣野好難比較啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幼女純軍事同用二戰作背景<br />\n後者都有軍事不過比幼女少，同埋成日賣女角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6fe8791e06e26b389d1d6e9738dd62c970e51be","tid":314043,"uid":1531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T16:36:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩樣野好難比較啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幼女純軍事同用二戰作背景<br />\n後者都有軍事不過比幼女少，同埋成日賣女角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n伊澤後面好唔好睇"},{"pid":"60c2436adcc18bf6d8f5a7af497b3b7b2f07d3a4","tid":314043,"uid":34622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T17:00:14.000Z","msg":"一套假幻女真軍事（連戰役細節都參考現實歷史）<br />\n一套假軍事真百合"},{"pid":"3a720793b105c2dbcffdceb9c9400818ed549a0e","tid":314043,"uid":1402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T17:00:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>伊澤塔高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n美中不足就係伊澤塔最後竟然唔使死<br />\n利申 無睇幼女</blockquote><br />\n平心而論 個ending都算完得幾好既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n何況吉野弘幸做劇本 一陣寫寫下暴走 出個垃圾ending咪仲慘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7013440f5a1620c80abd09806e3adb359dd7ad58","tid":314043,"uid":80323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T13:10:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩樣野好難比較啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\